      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $\\alpha \\in\\, ]0,\\pi[$ et\n$I_n =  \\int_{t=0}^\\pi \\frac{\\cos nt\\,d t}{1-\\sin\\alpha\\cos t} $.\n\nCalculer $I_n+I_{n+2}$ en fonction de $I_{n+1}$ puis\nexprimer $I_n$ en fonction de $\\alpha$ et $n$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha \\in\\, ]0,\\pi[\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I_n =  \\int_{t=0}^\\pi \\frac{\\cos nt\\,d t}{1-\\sin\\alpha\\cos t}\\)</span>.</p>\n<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I_n+I_{n+2}\\)</span> en fonction de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I_{n+1}\\)</span> puis exprimer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I_n\\)</span> en fonction de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "4afa8830-6f91-46e1-81c3-edcd91bbcd7a",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$I_n+I_{n+2} = \\frac{2I_{n+1}}{\\sin\\alpha}  \\Rightarrow \n          I_n = \\frac\\pi{\\cos\\alpha} \\Bigl(\\tan\\frac\\alpha2 \\Bigr)^n$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(I_n+I_{n+2} = \\frac{2I_{n+1}}{\\sin\\alpha}  \\Rightarrow \n          I_n = \\frac\\pi{\\cos\\alpha} \\Bigl(\\tan\\frac\\alpha2 \\Bigr)^n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
